name: newyear (10/10)
description:
a tiny shooter, made for day 10 of https://itch.io/jam/vmj2020

I did it! what a ride. 10 games in roughly 10 days (not consecutive days, clearly. but about 10 days of work!)

I made this one in 1 hour, to balance out all the time I spent on those bigger projects I did for the start of the jam.
